{"id": 6983, "title": "Ticket #6983: Python bindings: incorrect default argument for Collector.advertise", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn <code>collector.cpp</code>, the signature of <code>advertise</code> is\n\n<p></p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">void advertise(list ads, const std::string &amp;command_str=\"UPDATE_AD_GENERIC\", bool use_tcp=false)\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>but the docs state that <code>use_tcp</code> defaults to <code>True</code>. TJ believes that <code>True</code> is the correct default, so this ticket just changes the above signature to\n\n</p><p></p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">void advertise(list ads, const std::string &amp;command_str=\"UPDATE_AD_GENERIC\", bool use_tcp=true)\n</pre></div>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2019-Apr-11 16:13:50 by karpel:</em> <br/>\n\nReady for docs/review, except that we're in a docs freeze...\n\n<p>This should probably get mentioned in version history and upgrading from 8.8 to 8.10</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-May-06 15:50</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/8e31c54478821e4ff90f2dd907dda0ce3a02d5c0\">[56759]</a></span>: start 8.9.2 version history in new docs; set docs requirements.txt version to 8.9.1 add version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6963\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6963'); return false;\" title=\"Clean up argument names in the Python bindings\">#6963</a></span> and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6983\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper(